intent.user_query: what are the top 5 products based on revenue generated?

phases.goal: Calculate the revenue generated by each product in the fitness_db database.

key_arguments.sql: SELECT p.ProductName, SUM(sd.Quantity * sd.UnitPrice) AS Revenue FROM fitness_db.Products p JOIN fitness_db.SaleDetails sd ON p.ProductID = sd.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductName ORDER BY Revenue DESC;

phases.goal: Generate the final report displaying the top 5 products based on revenue.
